# StagePhoto.ru AI Rules
- ALWAYS follow docs/ai-context/*.md for design, tech, and routing decisions.
- NEVER use container mx-auto or max-width constraints on main sections. Full-bleed layout is mandatory.
- ALWAYS use Tailwind 4 syntax (@variant dark, @theme, CSS variables).
- ALWAYS default language to Russian (RU). Support EN/EO via localStorage + system detection.
- ALWAYS detect dark mode from OS preference first, then localStorage fallback.
- USE Livewire 4 islands, #[Url], wire:model.live, and Alpine $store for global state.
- USE Folio for routing: resources/views/pages/ maps directly to URLs.
- PRIORITIZE performance: lazy images, debounced filters, CSS grid masonry, minimal JS.
- NEVER generate promo fluff on homepage. Index = albums grid only.
- WHEN context overflows, reference docs/ai-context/00_INDEX.md first, then inject specific files.
